{"tid":755809,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲老豆老母到底做乜撚野？","createTime":"2018-07-25T13:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T14:32:04.000Z","uid":81587,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04d80426a27cfb1df8d2ef2b261ec451fdcb6883","tid":755809,"uid":81587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"做左補習都一段時間，發覺依家後生個輩啲父母都唔撚識點樣教小朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10個老豆老母有11個都想自己仔女入名校 <br />\n入名校唔係問題<br />\n問題係有冇諗過自己仔女夠唔夠班入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過有個老母要求我教佢個讀K2既女去間名小學interview 既英文對答 <br />\n重點係佢個女連A-Z都未識讀曬 未認得曬就要求一步登天要個女識英文對答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  未計個𡃁妹幼稚園讀左二年都仲係K2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且好多細路既老豆老母要求啲老師又要教到野又要俾貼紙、糖做獎勵，又要唔鬧得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂大佬 啲細路仔聽聽話話邊個想曬氣力鬧9你仔女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題係大部分細路上堂學野都係心散又掛住玩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算唔鬧 惡小小叫佢坐好啲專心小小都俾個老母話個小朋友好抗拒好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n縱到啲細路壞撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要指指點點啲老師點教 <br />\n咁撚多要求咁撚叻，不如你自己教啦<br />\n請我返黎托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我收你一舊水一個鐘仲要貼錢買埋貼紙俾你仔女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係條街到又由9啲𡃁仔係公眾場所橫衝直撞 <br />\n係香港人黎架 唔撚係蝗黎架<br />\n撞到人冇sorry、 2家人推住架bb車係啲小朋友面前講曬粗口開火 、打尖乜春都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再係咁落去 香港玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提外話 <br />\n依家啲補習中介公司真係不撚知所謂 以前都係收一兩堂錢做中介費<br />\n依家有啲過份到個個月都收你9% <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算個家長彈鐘補得一堂都照食你一半堂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係諗住幫人補既就私底下同家長deal好先 蝕都唔使蝕咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e4e4ec63c97be8d50833f7905b15a9cbd7f257","tid":755809,"uid":155725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"邊間9%？ 開名啦<br />\n<br />\n唔等錢洗就咪鬼做西客..."},{"pid":"935d4e2761ad4bae9bbe24ac8209d2a851729507","tid":755809,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"幫緊小學生補習 個老母日日問我個女有無機會入到個堆名校 又問我跨區無分加點樣問人借地址 又話逼個女入教會有分加 受洗又再加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬唔好咁痴線好無 雖然我知好多家長都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876ae4016bf0aacaa8b647346a72ee94e1bf0b01","tid":755809,"uid":102485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"聽個fd講 佢幫個國際學校嘅小學生補習<br />\n個家長話佢屋企個廁所唔外借<br />\n要我個fd落去樓下個商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11826124ab1bc455dd1988298bce85f49b6787fe","tid":755809,"uid":81587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876ae4016bf0aacaa8b647346a72ee94e1bf0b01","tid":755809,"uid":102485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"聽個fd講 佢幫個國際學校嘅小學生補習<br />\n個家長話佢屋企個廁所唔外借<br />\n要我個fd落去樓下個商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"哇屌咁撚仆街既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f0a2cf701a211e6eba983a3cd8d6a02cefce94","tid":755809,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"之前補個細佬<br />\n個中介係未補之前 打咗成個月電話黎交待<br />\n